              <operation>Get the index where the new type will be added to this object's list of possible types and then add it.</operation>
              <operation>Create the action for selecting this new type value, replacing the ampersand to display correctly and connecting its triggered signal.</operation>
              <operation>Add the new type selection action to the given menu.</operation>
              <return_description></return_description>
              <type>void</type>
            </data>
            <variable>
              <data>
