      <class>
        <data>
          <description>This is the singleton settings class that holds all global settings for C++/Qt projects. This class uses qt settings behind the scenes to make its setting persistent. As mentioned, it is also a single global class since it holds global settings.</description>
          <name>Settings</name>
        </data>
