      <class>
        <data>
          <description>This is the class block. This represents C++ classes. This inherits from the namespace block since a class expands upon the concept of a namespace. Because many properties of a class depend on the blocks it contains the class block is very dependent upon its child block properties.</description>
          <name>Class</name>
          <qtobject/>
        </data>
