            <name>makeCopy</name>
            <operation>Create a new blank block identical to this block's type.</operation>
            <operation>Make sure the new block is the same type.</operation>
            <operation>Copy this block's children and implementation data to the new block.</operation>
            <operation>Return the new block.</operation>
            <return_description>Exact copy of this block's data as a new block.</return_description>
